content.description: This is an eliminate of Garbage Compactor Sit. After matching the blocky hold off route the huge ledge out right and make a hard reach or throw up to a very cool pinch directly above.
content.location: Same start as Garbage Compactor sit, laying down under the roof with a left hand slightly under clinging crimp and a good right hand deep in the roof.

content.description: Crux is first move, from start position reaching up with right hand to grab sloper, them bump up to finger crimp and bread loaf jug. From here match with left hand and place feet on big ledge where hands were at start.
content.location: Start problem from sitting position with hands on the big jug ledge on the lower left of boulder. Place left heel on left side of boulder and right foot on a hold below ledge. Lift body from sitting into hanging/horizontal position. First move is Crux, reach up and back with right hand to sloper above, them bump right hand up to finger crimps and bread loaf jug, match with left hand. Place feet on big ledge where hands were at start. Continue to climb hands upwards and to the right toward the topmost corner of the boulder. Once hands are in place, move feet off ledge and to the right, planting right foot. Throw left feel on top of boulder and mantle to the top.

content.description: Add a hard very overhung thrutch to get into the start of the original line. A heel toe cam or two may prove useful (until the feet break).
content.location: Crawl under the boulder and find a left hand slightly under clinging crimp and a pretty good right hand crimp way back in the roof.

content.description: As short as they come, but sometimes that's nice. Basically one lock off to a jug ledge
content.location: Start on a left facing blocky hold using a wide choice of feet. Lock off to the huge ledge out left and top out.
